                                             season=season)

print(ats_record)
```

#### _pyespn.nfl.get_team_year_ats_away_underdog(team_id, season) ⇒_
returns a teams against the spread for a season as the away team and underdog

| Param   | Type | Description    |
|---------| --- |----------------|
