**example**

```python
from pyespn.nba import get_draft_pick_data

season = 2021
pick = 8
pick_round = 2

draft_pick_info = get_draft_pick_data(pick_round=pick_round,
                                      pick=pick,
                                      season=season)

print(draft_pick_info)
```



